1
00:00:18,705 --> 00:00:20,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad! Mom!</font>

2
00:00:20,905 --> 00:00:23,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Welcome home, Nao.
-You're looking healthy.</font>

3
00:00:25,638 --> 00:00:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing here?</font>

4
00:00:26,939 --> 00:00:28,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We were invited to a wedding.</font>

5
00:00:28,538 --> 00:00:30,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And we wanted to see you, Nao.</font>

6
00:00:30,972 --> 00:00:32,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you eating well?</font>

7
00:00:32,705 --> 00:00:34,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You look like you've lost a little weight.</font>

8
00:00:34,405 --> 00:00:36,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I'm perfectly fine.</font>

9
00:00:36,939 --> 00:00:39,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're going to come,
then you've got to tell me.</font>

10
00:00:39,738 --> 00:00:42,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your father wanted to surprise you.</font>

11
00:00:42,105 --> 00:00:43,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't need that kind of surprise.</font>

12
00:00:44,005 --> 00:00:45,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why not?</font>

13
00:00:45,405 --> 00:00:48,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you have a secret we'll find out
if we drop in suddenly?</font>

14
00:00:48,839 --> 00:00:52,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no...
Of course there's nothing like that.</font>

15
00:00:52,738 --> 00:00:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who is that?</font>

16
00:00:55,505 --> 00:00:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm... He's from school...</font>

17
00:01:00,738 --> 00:01:02,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean he's...</font>

18
00:01:03,405 --> 00:01:05,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Your homeroom teacher?
-Huh?</font>

19
00:01:05,405 --> 00:01:08,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, please.
That's obviously a school uniform.</font>

20
00:01:09,305 --> 00:01:14,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear me! I was just kidding.
He looks so adult-like.</font>

21
00:01:14,939 --> 00:01:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm... This is Uehara Hisashi.
He goes to the same school.</font>

22
00:01:20,138 --> 00:01:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He just happens to live
in the same building. Right?</font>

23
00:01:23,072 --> 00:01:27,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yes. Hello. Nice to meet you.
I'm Uehara.</font>

24
00:01:30,638 --> 00:01:34,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow, this is a really nice place,
isn't it?</font>

25
00:01:34,772 --> 00:01:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So this is your room.</font>

26
00:01:37,505 --> 00:01:41,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you know, the place is a real mess.</font>

27
00:01:41,338 --> 00:01:42,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, could you come back later?</font>

28
00:01:43,839 --> 00:01:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right!
Uehara works at a cafe near the station.</font>

29
00:01:47,472 --> 00:01:48,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't we all go there?</font>

30
00:01:48,738 --> 00:01:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

31
00:01:50,371 --> 00:01:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew it'd be a mess,
so I brought my apron.</font>

32
00:01:53,072 --> 00:01:55,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll clean the place up quickly
so we've got a place to sleep.</font>

33
00:01:55,805 --> 00:01:57,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yep.
-What?</font>

34
00:01:57,138 --> 00:01:59,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean you're staying the night here?</font>

35
00:01:59,972 --> 00:02:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course we are.</font>

36
00:02:01,905 --> 00:02:04,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No! No! Impossible! No way!</font>

37
00:02:04,772 --> 00:02:05,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

38
00:02:05,972 --> 00:02:08,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong with us staying
at our daughter's place?</font>

39
00:02:08,505 --> 00:02:12,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's nothing wrong with it,
but the place is so small.</font>

40
00:02:12,605 --> 00:02:15,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?
I thought you said it was quite large.</font>

41
00:02:16,438 --> 00:02:19,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! I don't have any comforters for you!</font>

42
00:02:19,072 --> 00:02:20,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

43
00:02:20,738 --> 00:02:23,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I rented comforters
so they'd arrive today.</font>

44
00:02:24,005 --> 00:02:27,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so convenient nowadays.
It's just a simple click on the Internet.</font>

45
00:02:27,705 --> 00:02:29,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Wait! Hold on a minute!</font>

46
00:02:29,072 --> 00:02:31,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to clean the place up!</font>

47
00:02:35,405 --> 00:02:38,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao, we don't care if it's a mess.</i></font>

48
00:02:38,438 --> 00:02:42,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said wait a minute! I <i>do care!</i></font>

49
00:03:17,538 --> 00:03:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">KING RAMEN</font>

50
00:03:25,305 --> 00:03:26,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MEN'S</font>

51
00:03:28,405 --> 00:03:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can't have this here.</font>

52
00:03:32,572 --> 00:03:33,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's no good.</font>

53
00:03:39,472 --> 00:03:41,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Such a beautiful place!</font>

54
00:03:41,939 --> 00:03:44,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is pretty big!</font>

55
00:03:44,105 --> 00:03:46,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've got to be kidding
if you think this is small!</font>

56
00:03:46,338 --> 00:03:49,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Come on in, Uehara.
-Oh, thank you.</font>

57
00:03:53,738 --> 00:03:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There are no mountains to look at,
so I don't feel quite at home.</font>

58
00:03:57,338 --> 00:03:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've forgotten
what it's like living in the city.</font>

59
00:03:59,672 --> 00:04:01,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right.</font>

60
00:04:01,939 --> 00:04:03,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">RULES</font>

61
00:04:03,839 --> 00:04:05,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Nao!</font>

62
00:04:05,638 --> 00:04:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There must be something wrong
with this place if it's only $800.</font>

63
00:04:10,505 --> 00:04:12,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's what I thought at first too.</font>

64
00:04:12,305 --> 00:04:14,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But they had reasons for it being $800.</font>

65
00:04:14,238 --> 00:04:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Reasons?</font>

66
00:04:16,072 --> 00:04:17,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, well...</font>

67
00:04:17,405 --> 00:04:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The landlady is a really nice person.</font>

68
00:04:20,238 --> 00:04:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'd love to meet her.</font>

69
00:04:23,072 --> 00:04:24,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, maybe next time.</font>

70
00:04:24,638 --> 00:04:25,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that your room, Nao?</font>

71
00:04:25,939 --> 00:04:26,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Oh!</font>

72
00:04:27,205 --> 00:04:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, my!</font>

73
00:04:30,672 --> 00:04:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look! You're keeping it so clean!</font>

74
00:04:35,805 --> 00:04:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think so?</font>

75
00:04:36,772 --> 00:04:40,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you're studying properly too, I see.</font>

76
00:04:41,005 --> 00:04:42,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, yeah.</font>

77
00:04:42,472 --> 00:04:44,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's this over here?</font>

78
00:04:44,638 --> 00:04:46,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Wait!</font>

79
00:04:46,572 --> 00:04:48,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is U...</font>

80
00:04:48,638 --> 00:04:50,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Uu?</font>

81
00:04:50,872 --> 00:04:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uu...
-Uu?</font>

82
00:04:52,271 --> 00:04:53,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Walk-in-closet!</font>

83
00:04:53,872 --> 00:04:56,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My! There sure is a lot of storage space.</font>

84
00:04:56,672 --> 00:04:58,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The closet walks?</font>

85
00:04:58,705 --> 00:05:00,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just where I keep extra stuff.</font>

86
00:05:00,738 --> 00:05:02,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a big mess, so don't you dare go in.</font>

87
00:05:02,805 --> 00:05:04,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK, OK.
-I can at least have a look?</font>

88
00:05:04,705 --> 00:05:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad! This is my own place, OK?</font>

89
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:10,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine.</font>

90
00:05:11,105 --> 00:05:11,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

91
00:05:12,405 --> 00:05:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, uhm... This is mental training.</font>

92
00:05:19,405 --> 00:05:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ah!
-Huh? What?</font>

93
00:05:21,905 --> 00:05:23,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's the matter?</font>

94
00:05:23,305 --> 00:05:25,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I got a little light-headed.
-Really? Are you OK?</font>

95
00:05:25,738 --> 00:05:27,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Paper! Here!
-Paper hair?</font>

96
00:05:28,005 --> 00:05:29,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On the floor!</font>

97
00:05:32,505 --> 00:05:33,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you all right?</font>

98
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:37,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'm fine. It was nothing.</font>

99
00:05:37,171 --> 00:05:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's good to hear.</font>

100
00:05:38,672 --> 00:05:42,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're awfully young
to be getting light-headed.</font>

101
00:05:42,171 --> 00:05:43,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're absolutely right.</font>

102
00:05:46,572 --> 00:05:47,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Men's"?</font>

103
00:05:50,171 --> 00:05:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's this, Nao?</font>

104
00:05:52,138 --> 00:05:53,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I... uh...</font>

105
00:05:53,872 --> 00:05:58,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. That dumb friend
of yours is into that, right?</font>

106
00:05:58,972 --> 00:05:59,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dumb friend?</font>

107
00:06:00,738 --> 00:06:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, I mean...</font>

108
00:06:02,672 --> 00:06:05,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's good friend...</font>

109
00:06:11,939 --> 00:06:13,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to use your restroom!</font>

110
00:06:16,338 --> 00:06:18,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! This is the bath!</font>

111
00:06:18,205 --> 00:06:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My place has the same layout.
The toilet is over there.</font>

112
00:06:20,238 --> 00:06:21,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Hurry! Hurry!</font>

113
00:06:21,505 --> 00:06:23,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!</font>

114
00:06:52,305 --> 00:06:54,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go.</font>

115
00:06:54,371 --> 00:06:57,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here you are, Uehara.
-Thank you.</font>

116
00:06:58,505 --> 00:07:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I'd known
there was such a handsome guy here,</font>

117
00:07:01,171 --> 00:07:04,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I would have brought a souvenir.</font>

118
00:07:05,205 --> 00:07:08,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, instead of a souvenir,</font>

119
00:07:08,638 --> 00:07:12,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I <i>do have my special croquettes.</i></font>

120
00:07:13,338 --> 00:07:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told her not to bring them
because they're just extra weight.</font>

121
00:07:16,072 --> 00:07:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She wanted you to have them so badly,
she got up at three o'clock.</font>

122
00:07:19,638 --> 00:07:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I guess I could have made them here.</font>

123
00:07:22,072 --> 00:07:24,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't know if I'd have time
or the utensils to do it.</font>

124
00:07:25,138 --> 00:07:26,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They look delicious, don't they?</font>

125
00:07:27,138 --> 00:07:29,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After eating these,
I decided to marry her.</font>

126
00:07:30,005 --> 00:07:32,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Not that story again.</font>

127
00:07:32,505 --> 00:07:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad always tells this story
when Mom makes croquettes.</font>

128
00:07:35,438 --> 00:07:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made a lot of other
more difficult dishes, didn't I?</font>

129
00:07:38,371 --> 00:07:42,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it was the croquettes
that won over my stomach.</font>

130
00:07:43,039 --> 00:07:45,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't get croquettes better
than this anywhere.</font>

131
00:07:45,538 --> 00:07:48,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And they're even better
since they're made with potatoes we grew.</font>

132
00:07:48,905 --> 00:07:50,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here, have one.</font>

133
00:07:50,705 --> 00:07:51,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I can't, really.</font>

134
00:07:52,438 --> 00:07:55,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please, help yourself. I can make more.</font>

135
00:07:55,138 --> 00:07:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It appears she's cooking for herself,
so I've got all the things I need here.</font>

136
00:07:59,371 --> 00:08:02,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mom,
you've got to teach me how to make these.</font>

137
00:08:02,238 --> 00:08:05,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Have you gotten a boyfriend?</font>

138
00:08:06,738 --> 00:08:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way that's possible,
right, Nao?</font>

139
00:08:10,472 --> 00:08:13,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh... yeah.</font>

140
00:08:13,438 --> 00:08:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just can't recreate the taste of these.</font>

141
00:08:16,072 --> 00:08:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course not.
You see, it's my trade secret!</font>

142
00:08:20,138 --> 00:08:21,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

143
00:08:24,605 --> 00:08:30,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, are you one of Nao's schoolmates?</font>

144
00:08:30,872 --> 00:08:32,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Schoolmates?</font>

145
00:08:32,839 --> 00:08:34,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We have different homerooms.</font>

146
00:08:34,872 --> 00:08:37,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you live here with your family?</font>

147
00:08:37,972 --> 00:08:41,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I live away from my family.</font>

148
00:08:41,772 --> 00:08:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara lives alone too.</font>

149
00:08:44,072 --> 00:08:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

150
00:08:46,171 --> 00:08:48,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you often...</font>

151
00:08:50,271 --> 00:08:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">come here to visit?</font>

152
00:08:55,472 --> 00:08:56,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is my first time.</font>

153
00:08:57,472 --> 00:09:00,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

154
00:09:00,572 --> 00:09:05,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara is so busy with work
that he hardly ever comes home.</font>

155
00:09:05,672 --> 00:09:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He leaves early in the morning
and comes home late</font>

156
00:09:07,738 --> 00:09:10,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so he goes straight to bed
when he gets home, right?</font>

157
00:09:10,238 --> 00:09:11,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure know him well.</font>

158
00:09:12,839 --> 00:09:14,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh... well...</font>

159
00:09:15,572 --> 00:09:18,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We sometimes come home from work
at the same time.</font>

160
00:09:19,672 --> 00:09:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That reminds me,</font>

161
00:09:20,605 --> 00:09:23,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you're working at a ramen shop,
aren't you, Nao?</font>

162
00:09:23,238 --> 00:09:26,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd really like to see you at work there.</font>

163
00:09:31,605 --> 00:09:33,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, sorry, it's nothing.</font>

164
00:09:37,105 --> 00:09:39,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The ramen is so good
that it makes you laugh, isn't it?</font>

165
00:09:39,872 --> 00:09:43,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">With having to work morning and night,</font>

166
00:09:43,238 --> 00:09:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">are your grades all right?</font>

167
00:09:46,072 --> 00:09:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uehara's at the top of the class.
-Really?</font>

168
00:09:48,772 --> 00:09:50,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! That's amazing!</font>

169
00:09:50,905 --> 00:09:53,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, you should have Uehara be your tutor.</font>

170
00:09:53,305 --> 00:09:54,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Ow! That's hot!</font>

171
00:09:54,371 --> 00:09:56,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, dear! Oh, dear!
-What are you talking about?</font>

172
00:09:59,939 --> 00:10:02,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Are you OK, Dad?
-Yeah, I'm sorry.</font>

173
00:10:04,305 --> 00:10:07,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, I've got to get to work pretty soon.</font>

174
00:10:08,005 --> 00:10:09,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. That's right.</font>

175
00:10:12,271 --> 00:10:13,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on a minute.</font>

176
00:10:16,438 --> 00:10:19,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You said that this was the first time
you've been here.</font>

177
00:10:20,105 --> 00:10:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

178
00:10:24,538 --> 00:10:27,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you know this had tissues in it?</font>

179
00:10:29,505 --> 00:10:32,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This looks like nothing more
than a stuffed animal!</font>

180
00:10:38,472 --> 00:10:43,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually, he does sometimes
come help me study</font>

181
00:10:44,405 --> 00:10:46,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and has dinner here.</font>

182
00:10:48,572 --> 00:10:49,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm very sorry.</font>

183
00:10:50,005 --> 00:10:51,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Huh?</font>

184
00:10:51,072 --> 00:10:53,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing, Uehara?</font>

185
00:10:55,105 --> 00:10:58,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao and I are dating.</font>

186
00:11:04,905 --> 00:11:08,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, really? You should have told us, Nao.</font>

187
00:11:09,505 --> 00:11:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we only started just recently.</font>

188
00:11:14,438 --> 00:11:16,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was a surprise.</font>

189
00:11:16,205 --> 00:11:18,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm the one who's surprised.</i></font>

190
00:11:18,171 --> 00:11:21,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong with you?
Why didn't you say so?</font>

191
00:11:21,738 --> 00:11:24,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry.
-There's no need to apologize.</font>

192
00:11:24,705 --> 00:11:27,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so happy that Nao's got a boyfriend.</font>

193
00:11:27,238 --> 00:11:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, Uehara. Time to go to work, right?</font>

194
00:11:30,271 --> 00:11:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, but I've still got things to say.</font>

195
00:11:32,271 --> 00:11:35,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Her father's a bit flustered right now.
Let's go.</font>

196
00:11:39,238 --> 00:11:40,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to pull myself together.</font>

197
00:11:56,572 --> 00:11:58,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait right there!</font>

198
00:12:09,939 --> 00:12:11,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want an explanation.</font>

199
00:12:12,438 --> 00:12:13,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm very sorry.</font>

200
00:12:18,572 --> 00:12:23,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We were the victims
of a double-contract scam</font>

201
00:12:24,839 --> 00:12:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and just happened to move in here
on the exact same day.</font>

202
00:12:28,072 --> 00:12:29,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A scam!</font>

203
00:12:29,505 --> 00:12:32,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why didn't you tell us about
such an important thing?</font>

204
00:12:32,705 --> 00:12:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't want to cause you
any extra worry.</font>

205
00:12:36,271 --> 00:12:38,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Extra worry?
-No matter the reason,</font>

206
00:12:39,905 --> 00:12:42,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you kept it secret from your parents,
that you're living with another student.</font>

207
00:12:43,205 --> 00:12:45,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will never allow it.</font>

208
00:12:48,338 --> 00:12:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm taking Nao back home with us.</font>

209
00:12:50,972 --> 00:12:53,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll worry about the rest later.</font>

210
00:12:53,939 --> 00:12:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad!</font>

211
00:12:54,839 --> 00:12:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is exactly why I was opposed
to you living alone in the first place!</font>

212
00:12:58,472 --> 00:13:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, it's a little late now--</font>

213
00:13:00,371 --> 00:13:03,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This wouldn't have happened
if you hadn't approved of it.</font>

214
00:13:03,105 --> 00:13:07,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Are you saying this is my fault?</font>

215
00:13:07,438 --> 00:13:10,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one who said
that she'd have problems in the future</font>

216
00:13:10,205 --> 00:13:11,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">if she didn't learn how to cook and clean.</font>

217
00:13:11,772 --> 00:13:14,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you said she should
experience living on her own!</font>

218
00:13:14,238 --> 00:13:17,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said living <i>alone was OK,
not living <i>with a guy!</i></i></font>

219
00:13:17,405 --> 00:13:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why are you getting angry at me?</font>

220
00:13:20,238 --> 00:13:23,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you've always spoiled Nao.</font>

221
00:13:23,438 --> 00:13:26,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the last person
I want to hear that from.</font>

222
00:13:26,405 --> 00:13:27,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

223
00:13:27,338 --> 00:13:30,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one who always spoiled Nao!</font>

224
00:13:30,405 --> 00:13:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'd give her spending money
without telling me</font>

225
00:13:32,672 --> 00:13:34,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and let her eat as much candy
as she wanted.</font>

226
00:13:34,672 --> 00:13:38,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to that,
Nao's always had tons of cavities.</font>

227
00:13:38,105 --> 00:13:40,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why are we talking about this?
-Cut it out!</font>

228
00:13:40,438 --> 00:13:41,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will leave.</font>

229
00:13:41,939 --> 00:13:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Uehara?</font>

230
00:13:46,638 --> 00:13:49,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go back to my home
for the time being.</font>

231
00:13:51,738 --> 00:13:53,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I apologize for all of this.</font>

232
00:14:20,638 --> 00:14:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want an explanation.</font>

233
00:14:24,638 --> 00:14:26,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I already told you.</font>

234
00:14:26,939 --> 00:14:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't talk to me like that.</font>

235
00:14:29,271 --> 00:14:31,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you won't believe me
no matter what I say, Dad!</font>

236
00:14:32,005 --> 00:14:33,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

237
00:14:33,238 --> 00:14:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's exactly because I believe you
that I want to know the truth.</font>

238
00:14:36,271 --> 00:14:39,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you sleeping
with that scrawny guy?</font>

239
00:14:39,338 --> 00:14:40,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not sleeping together. Living together.</font>

240
00:14:40,839 --> 00:14:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's the same.
-No, it's not.</font>

241
00:14:42,972 --> 00:14:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't pay the $1,500 rent,
so it couldn't be helped.</font>

242
00:14:45,371 --> 00:14:46,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Couldn't be helped?</font>

243
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're being deceived by him!
Wake up to that fact, would you?</font>

244
00:14:50,438 --> 00:14:52,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara isn't that kind of person!</font>

245
00:14:52,638 --> 00:14:56,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everybody knows that handsome guys
are rotten at the core.</font>

246
00:14:56,072 --> 00:14:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?
You're just jealous!</font>

247
00:14:58,972 --> 00:15:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeal... What are you talking about?</font>

248
00:15:01,138 --> 00:15:03,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I may not be now,
but I used to be pretty darn good looking!</font>

249
00:15:03,905 --> 00:15:05,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who cares about that?</font>

250
00:15:05,839 --> 00:15:06,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're changing the subject!</font>

251
00:15:06,972 --> 00:15:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At any rate, I will not allow it, ever!</font>

252
00:15:10,371 --> 00:15:12,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But if you insist on continuing
to live here...</font>

253
00:15:13,939 --> 00:15:15,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">then I'll sever our ties with you!</font>

254
00:15:16,438 --> 00:15:17,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dear!</font>

255
00:15:17,939 --> 00:15:20,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you still want to live with him
after that, then do what you like!</font>

256
00:15:29,271 --> 00:15:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate you, Dad!</font>

257
00:15:33,638 --> 00:15:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">CAFE</font>

258
00:15:42,805 --> 00:15:43,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

259
00:15:45,305 --> 00:15:47,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh no! What're you doing?</font>

260
00:15:47,705 --> 00:15:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was rejected again.</font>

261
00:15:56,371 --> 00:15:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Holy crap!</i></font>

262
00:15:57,271 --> 00:15:58,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's worse than me getting rejected.</font>

263
00:15:58,872 --> 00:16:00,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A million times worse.</font>

264
00:16:00,905 --> 00:16:04,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's rough!
It would be bad enough</font>

265
00:16:04,138 --> 00:16:07,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">meeting your girlfriend's parents
under normal circumstances.</font>

266
00:16:07,805 --> 00:16:09,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, that's what it's like?</font>

267
00:16:09,371 --> 00:16:13,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Well, I've never had that chance.
-I didn't think so.</font>

268
00:16:13,638 --> 00:16:15,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But my own mom,</font>

269
00:16:15,972 --> 00:16:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she'd be totally happy
if I got a girlfriend.</font>

270
00:16:22,072 --> 00:16:25,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, sorry.
-About what?</font>

271
00:16:28,105 --> 00:16:31,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But seriously, though,
what are you going to do?</font>

272
00:16:33,338 --> 00:16:35,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's a room open on the second floor
at one of my jobs.</font>

273
00:16:36,072 --> 00:16:39,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So at least I've got a place to move to.</font>

274
00:16:41,205 --> 00:16:42,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure that's OK?</font>

275
00:16:43,438 --> 00:16:46,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, Nao was in quite a panic.</font>

276
00:16:47,839 --> 00:16:51,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I mean, are <i>you going to be OK?
-Huh?</i></font>

277
00:16:52,338 --> 00:16:54,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll be separated from Nao.</font>

278
00:16:57,338 --> 00:17:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But if Nao's free,</font>

279
00:17:01,271 --> 00:17:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">maybe I'll ask her to date me again.</font>

280
00:17:06,238 --> 00:17:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!</font>

281
00:17:08,572 --> 00:17:11,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That seriously hurt, Uehara!</font>

282
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

283
00:17:13,772 --> 00:17:15,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow, that really hurt.</font>

284
00:17:30,138 --> 00:17:31,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHIKAWA NAO</font>

285
00:17:39,405 --> 00:17:43,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! It finally happened.
So what did your parents say?</font>

286
00:17:43,605 --> 00:17:48,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My dad was totally pissed off.
He said he's taking me back home.</font>

287
00:17:48,872 --> 00:17:50,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

288
00:17:51,472 --> 00:17:55,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! That means you'll transfer out!
No! Please don't do that!</font>

289
00:17:55,072 --> 00:17:56,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want that either!</font>

290
00:17:57,039 --> 00:18:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he said he'd sever relations with me
if I didn't.</font>

291
00:18:00,505 --> 00:18:03,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! That's brutal.</font>

292
00:18:03,472 --> 00:18:04,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about your mom?</font>

293
00:18:05,205 --> 00:18:09,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's odd. Mom's awfully cool about it.
It's actually kind of scary.</font>

294
00:18:10,171 --> 00:18:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I guess it makes sense.</font>

295
00:18:12,605 --> 00:18:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No girl's parents are OK
with their daughter living with a guy.</font>

296
00:18:19,939 --> 00:18:21,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know what to do.</font>

297
00:18:23,905 --> 00:18:27,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In any case,
one of you should probably move.</font>

298
00:18:27,205 --> 00:18:30,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Though that won't settle everything.</font>

299
00:18:31,972 --> 00:18:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about Uehara? What's he doing now?</font>

300
00:18:35,738 --> 00:18:37,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He went to his brother's
for the time being.</font>

301
00:18:39,538 --> 00:18:41,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

302
00:18:46,872 --> 00:18:51,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't see him at home
and at school on break.</font>

303
00:18:55,205 --> 00:18:57,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Must be lonely.</font>

304
00:18:58,872 --> 00:19:02,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And it's going to be like this
for a long time too, right?</font>

305
00:19:04,472 --> 00:19:07,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you and him have it good.</font>

306
00:19:08,839 --> 00:19:11,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When school's on break</font>

307
00:19:11,438 --> 00:19:15,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi and I can only meet
once every three days.</font>

308
00:19:16,772 --> 00:19:19,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess we've had it too good until now.</font>

309
00:19:20,572 --> 00:19:21,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep.</font>

310
00:19:27,405 --> 00:19:29,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the landlady.</font>

311
00:19:34,438 --> 00:19:35,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'd better answer.</font>

312
00:19:42,138 --> 00:19:43,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

313
00:19:44,538 --> 00:19:46,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao works real hard.</i></font>

314
00:19:46,438 --> 00:19:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's our shop's fresh young face.</font>

315
00:19:48,772 --> 00:19:50,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you must be kidding.</font>

316
00:19:50,371 --> 00:19:53,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At home, she always left the place a mess.</font>

317
00:19:53,605 --> 00:19:56,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And even when she occasionally
helped me with cooking,</font>

318
00:19:56,205 --> 00:19:59,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she'd break dishes and cut her fingers.</font>

319
00:19:59,238 --> 00:20:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She broke a ton when she first started.</font>

320
00:20:01,572 --> 00:20:03,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But lately she's down to breaking
only one a day.</font>

321
00:20:03,972 --> 00:20:05,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

322
00:20:05,405 --> 00:20:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd love to have her
as my daughter-in-law.</font>

323
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:09,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, come on, Dad!
-I'm just saying</font>

324
00:20:09,205 --> 00:20:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that how good she is.</font>

325
00:20:11,271 --> 00:20:14,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She really is honest,
serious and a great worker.</font>

326
00:20:14,338 --> 00:20:17,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so glad to hear that.</font>

327
00:20:18,039 --> 00:20:20,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Would you like a <i>kaedama, sir?</i></font>

328
00:20:20,605 --> 00:20:21,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that?</font>

329
00:20:22,138 --> 00:20:24,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A refill. He'll fill your bowl
with more ramen, right?</font>

330
00:20:24,839 --> 00:20:25,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

331
00:20:26,338 --> 00:20:28,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'll have a <i>kaedama.</i></font>

332
00:20:28,705 --> 00:20:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-One <i>kaedama!
-Coming right up!</i></font>

333
00:20:36,672 --> 00:20:39,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just look at that smile!</font>

334
00:20:40,371 --> 00:20:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All Nao's friends have become
regular customers.</font>

335
00:20:42,972 --> 00:20:43,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really appreciate it.</font>

336
00:20:58,738 --> 00:21:00,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Dad!
-What?</font>

337
00:21:00,939 --> 00:21:04,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you told the landlady
you're cancelling the contract?</font>

338
00:21:05,672 --> 00:21:07,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This isn't just <i>my home.</i></font>

339
00:21:07,805 --> 00:21:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All I told her was that you're leaving.</font>

340
00:21:10,171 --> 00:21:11,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he wants to live here, then he can.</font>

341
00:21:11,972 --> 00:21:14,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Uehara's got special circumstances.</font>

342
00:21:14,205 --> 00:21:15,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I care?</font>

343
00:21:15,972 --> 00:21:18,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you don't care what happens to Uehara?</font>

344
00:21:18,839 --> 00:21:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It has nothing to do with our family.</font>

345
00:21:22,705 --> 00:21:23,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're awful.</font>

346
00:21:24,338 --> 00:21:25,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

347
00:21:25,538 --> 00:21:27,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate your guts, Dad!</font>

348
00:21:28,638 --> 00:21:31,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Where are you going, Nao?
-I don't care. Anywhere but here.</font>

349
00:21:31,772 --> 00:21:34,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way
I'm going back home with Dad!</font>

350
00:21:34,505 --> 00:21:35,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

351
00:21:36,005 --> 00:21:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dear!</font>

352
00:21:37,371 --> 00:21:39,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's none of my concern.
Let her do what she wants.</font>

353
00:21:39,438 --> 00:21:41,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dear!</font>

354
00:21:50,638 --> 00:21:52,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">CAFE</font>

355
00:22:04,371 --> 00:22:05,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

356
00:22:06,638 --> 00:22:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

357
00:22:12,105 --> 00:22:13,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing here?</font>

358
00:22:16,538 --> 00:22:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I ran away.
-What?</font>

359
00:22:21,538 --> 00:22:22,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come over here.</font>

360
00:22:23,572 --> 00:22:24,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>What the hell are you thinking?</i></font>

361
00:22:24,872 --> 00:22:27,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Dad says he's going to cancel
the rental agreement</i></font>

362
00:22:27,772 --> 00:22:29,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>and take me back home.</i></font>

363
00:22:30,039 --> 00:22:31,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way I'll stand for that!</font>

364
00:22:32,338 --> 00:22:33,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

365
00:22:34,972 --> 00:22:37,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me stay at your brother's place.</font>

366
00:22:38,472 --> 00:22:40,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want to see my dad anymore.</font>

367
00:22:41,171 --> 00:22:44,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's talking about severing relations
with me if we keep living together.</font>

368
00:22:44,972 --> 00:22:46,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I will sever relations with <i>him!</i></i></font>

369
00:22:46,839 --> 00:22:47,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That stupid blockhead!</font>

370
00:22:58,305 --> 00:22:59,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm taking you back to the apartment.</font>

371
00:23:02,039 --> 00:23:04,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Go back.</font>

372
00:23:09,338 --> 00:23:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean you're all right
with me going back to my parents' place?</font>

373
00:23:18,405 --> 00:23:20,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, you won't be lonely?</font>

374
00:23:22,972 --> 00:23:25,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're OK with not seeing me anymore?</font>

375
00:23:27,972 --> 00:23:30,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you won't say anything?</font>

376
00:23:31,872 --> 00:23:34,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Am I the only one
who wants to stay together forever?</font>

377
00:23:34,405 --> 00:23:35,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

378
00:23:37,905 --> 00:23:40,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want you to run away from home.</font>

379
00:23:42,371 --> 00:23:45,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to go back
and apologize to your father.</font>

380
00:23:45,672 --> 00:23:47,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No.
-Nao!</font>

381
00:23:51,738 --> 00:23:54,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't ever say you'll sever relations
with your parents.</font>

382
00:24:03,905 --> 00:24:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be thinking about
what to do for our future too.</font>

383
00:24:19,638 --> 00:24:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK?</font>

384
00:24:59,338 --> 00:25:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome.</font>

385
00:25:01,371 --> 00:25:05,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Just a party of one.
-Go ahead. Sit wherever you like.</font>

386
00:25:10,939 --> 00:25:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm home.
-Oh, hi.</font>

387
00:25:13,472 --> 00:25:16,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Hey Dad, where's Uehara?</font>

388
00:25:16,305 --> 00:25:18,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, now that you mention it,
he's not here yet.</font>

389
00:25:18,772 --> 00:25:20,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aw, darn it all.</font>

390
00:25:22,138 --> 00:25:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. Hello.</font>

391
00:25:28,105 --> 00:25:31,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for waiting. Here you are.</font>

392
00:25:31,605 --> 00:25:34,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, is that Uehara you mentioned
Uehara Hisashi?</font>

393
00:25:34,839 --> 00:25:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. Oh, are you an acquaintance?</font>

394
00:25:37,672 --> 00:25:39,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, uh, yes.</font>

395
00:25:40,039 --> 00:25:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you a relative of his?</font>

396
00:25:41,905 --> 00:25:43,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah... uh, yes, kind of...</font>

397
00:25:43,872 --> 00:25:47,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, is that so? What a surprise.</font>

398
00:25:47,171 --> 00:25:49,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nice to meet you. I'm Kusanagi.</font>

399
00:25:51,072 --> 00:25:55,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, he's a really hard worker.</font>

400
00:25:56,138 --> 00:25:58,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I worry about him,</font>

401
00:25:58,805 --> 00:26:02,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so sometimes I feel like
I should treat him like I were his father.</font>

402
00:26:02,705 --> 00:26:04,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like his father?</font>

403
00:26:04,305 --> 00:26:06,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'm sorry.
That was awfully presumptuous of me.</font>

404
00:26:06,939 --> 00:26:09,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't know he had any relatives nearby.</font>

405
00:26:09,138 --> 00:26:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK.</font>

406
00:26:10,171 --> 00:26:11,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

407
00:26:12,872 --> 00:26:15,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When I heard that his parents died
when he was little</font>

408
00:26:15,305 --> 00:26:17,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and he was an orphan,</font>

409
00:26:17,805 --> 00:26:21,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wondered if there was any way
that I could help him.</font>

410
00:26:22,538 --> 00:26:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, but he does have an older brother.</font>

411
00:26:25,572 --> 00:26:28,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he's already got a family of his own,</font>

412
00:26:28,438 --> 00:26:30,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and he's going to be transferred
overseas soon.</font>

413
00:26:32,205 --> 00:26:35,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's not that easy to do what he does.</font>

414
00:26:35,072 --> 00:26:39,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Earning money to live off of by himself...
And he's got great grades as well.</font>

415
00:26:40,505 --> 00:26:43,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's so serious and a hard worker.</font>

416
00:26:58,305 --> 00:26:59,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

417
00:27:09,939 --> 00:27:11,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's from the cafe.</font>

418
00:27:14,205 --> 00:27:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go ahead and go to work.</font>

419
00:27:17,472 --> 00:27:20,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry. I'll go back like you said.</font>

420
00:27:24,238 --> 00:27:27,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be fine. Thank you.</font>

421
00:27:44,005 --> 00:27:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I can't do this.</font>

422
00:27:46,772 --> 00:27:48,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao.</i></font>

423
00:27:51,638 --> 00:27:52,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mom.</font>

424
00:27:58,805 --> 00:28:01,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome home, Nao.</font>

425
00:28:08,572 --> 00:28:10,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you'd run away from home.</font>

426
00:28:13,972 --> 00:28:16,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara told me to come back.</font>

427
00:28:18,405 --> 00:28:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I have no intention
of going back home with you.</font>

428
00:28:22,605 --> 00:28:25,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to graduate from this high school.</font>

429
00:28:26,405 --> 00:28:29,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I don't want to leave my friends.</font>

430
00:28:30,505 --> 00:28:31,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dear,</font>

431
00:28:31,905 --> 00:28:36,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm against forcing Nao to come back home.</font>

432
00:28:37,572 --> 00:28:38,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mom.</font>

433
00:28:39,672 --> 00:28:43,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't forgive you for not telling us
that you were living with him,</font>

434
00:28:45,005 --> 00:28:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I know that there were
unavoidable circumstances for both of you.</font>

435
00:28:49,405 --> 00:28:50,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What circumstances?</font>

436
00:28:51,772 --> 00:28:57,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara lost his parents
when he was little,</font>

437
00:28:58,138 --> 00:29:01,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and his only family is his older brother.</font>

438
00:29:02,138 --> 00:29:04,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you find that out?</font>

439
00:29:05,405 --> 00:29:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why didn't you tell us that before?</font>

440
00:29:09,305 --> 00:29:11,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That the both of you
started living together</font>

441
00:29:12,605 --> 00:29:15,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">only after worrying a lot over
whether you should.</font>

442
00:29:23,005 --> 00:29:26,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm asking you too, dear.</font>

443
00:29:27,238 --> 00:29:30,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want you to do anything rash</font>

444
00:29:30,072 --> 00:29:32,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">like forcing her to suddenly move out
like this.</font>

445
00:29:39,939 --> 00:29:41,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think</font>

446
00:29:42,171 --> 00:29:46,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we should spend a little more time
before coming to a decision about this.</font>

447
00:29:47,538 --> 00:29:48,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Mom.</font>

448
00:29:53,072 --> 00:29:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to trust you, Nao.</font>

449
00:30:06,338 --> 00:30:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, dear,</font>

450
00:30:08,438 --> 00:30:11,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you're unhappy just because
Nao got herself a boyfriend, right?</font>

451
00:30:14,105 --> 00:30:17,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, fathers will always</font>

452
00:30:17,205 --> 00:30:21,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">object to whatever boys
their daughters bring home.</font>

453
00:30:21,672 --> 00:30:24,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And it's even worse
the more handsome he is.</font>

454
00:30:26,105 --> 00:30:29,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! You women always end up
conspiring together so easily.</font>

455
00:30:30,105 --> 00:30:33,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You may have succeeded
in sweet-talking your mother into this,</font>

456
00:30:33,238 --> 00:30:34,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but you won't be able to win me over
so easily.</font>

457
00:30:35,005 --> 00:30:38,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I haven't sweet-talked her at all.</font>

458
00:30:38,305 --> 00:30:40,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.
You always get suspicious so easily.</font>

459
00:30:41,505 --> 00:30:42,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't stand this.</font>

460
00:30:43,538 --> 00:30:45,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where are you going?
We'll be having dinner soon.</font>

461
00:30:45,705 --> 00:30:48,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I won't need it.
-Dad!</font>

462
00:30:53,405 --> 00:30:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">CAFE</font>

463
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Manager.
-Uh-huh?</font>

464
00:31:08,638 --> 00:31:09,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry,</font>

465
00:31:10,005 --> 00:31:12,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but can I finish up now today?</font>

466
00:31:12,305 --> 00:31:13,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure. What's up?</font>

467
00:31:15,039 --> 00:31:17,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's someone that I have to talk to.</font>

468
00:31:26,972 --> 00:31:28,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome!</font>

469
00:31:49,238 --> 00:31:52,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just on my way to go talk to you.</font>

470
00:31:53,072 --> 00:31:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you think you could have a proper talk
on an empty stomach?</font>

471
00:31:58,438 --> 00:31:59,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right.</font>

472
00:32:01,238 --> 00:32:02,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're very frank.</font>

473
00:32:04,538 --> 00:32:05,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

474
00:32:08,538 --> 00:32:09,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

475
00:32:10,672 --> 00:32:11,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Croquettes again?</font>

476
00:32:12,039 --> 00:32:16,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">These are the best way
to put your father in a good mood.</font>

477
00:32:16,505 --> 00:32:21,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, you want to learn how to make
the Yoshikawa special croquette, right?</font>

478
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:24,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah!
-Yeah!</font>

479
00:32:26,271 --> 00:32:27,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! That's hot!</font>

480
00:32:27,772 --> 00:32:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, you! Here, use a washcloth.
-Okay.</font>

481
00:32:30,572 --> 00:32:34,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Those will burn you.
-Thank you.</font>

482
00:32:36,205 --> 00:32:39,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think your father can understand
the difficulties Uehara's going through.</font>

483
00:32:51,538 --> 00:32:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My father was completely opposed
to me going to university.</font>

484
00:32:57,438 --> 00:33:01,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I wanted to go to university
in Tokyo so badly</font>

485
00:33:01,738 --> 00:33:03,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so I ran away from home.</font>

486
00:33:05,338 --> 00:33:09,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When I was a student, I had to earn
my tuition and everything myself.</font>

487
00:33:10,772 --> 00:33:12,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Back then, that was the norm.</font>

488
00:33:14,138 --> 00:33:18,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But now, it's different for students.</font>

489
00:33:20,238 --> 00:33:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'm not old enough.</font>

490
00:33:21,672 --> 00:33:26,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right.
You're still in high school.</font>

491
00:33:26,572 --> 00:33:27,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, still.</font>

492
00:33:36,538 --> 00:33:38,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here we go!
-What?</font>

493
00:33:39,338 --> 00:33:41,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For the Yoshikawa family
special croquettes,</font>

494
00:33:41,805 --> 00:33:45,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I put in a little bit
of whipping cream here.</font>

495
00:33:45,839 --> 00:33:49,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! So that's the secret
behind their fluffiness!</font>

496
00:33:50,805 --> 00:33:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear! I've given away
your mother's trade secret!</font>

497
00:34:11,338 --> 00:34:13,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Mom?
-Uh-huh?</font>

498
00:34:17,972 --> 00:34:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

499
00:34:26,271 --> 00:34:28,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You said</font>

500
00:34:28,305 --> 00:34:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you didn't want to cause us
any extra worry because of the scam.</font>

501
00:34:33,171 --> 00:34:36,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, you see, parents want extra worry.</font>

502
00:34:38,638 --> 00:34:42,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Think of how lonely I'd be
if you didn't cause me to worry.</font>

503
00:34:46,405 --> 00:34:47,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Mom.</font>

504
00:34:48,772 --> 00:34:52,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You want to keep living here with Uehara,
don't you, Nao?</font>

505
00:34:55,105 --> 00:34:56,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

506
00:34:59,472 --> 00:35:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All right.</font>

507
00:35:02,939 --> 00:35:05,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I want you to make me one promise.</font>

508
00:35:09,138 --> 00:35:12,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Promise me
that you won't lie to me anymore.</font>

509
00:35:15,738 --> 00:35:19,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From now on I'll listen carefully
to what you have to say</font>

510
00:35:20,171 --> 00:35:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and worry with you,
and think things over with you.</font>

511
00:35:23,972 --> 00:35:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I want you to talk to me
about anything important in your life.</font>

512
00:35:31,039 --> 00:35:32,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

513
00:35:33,538 --> 00:35:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good.</font>

514
00:35:35,672 --> 00:35:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All right.
